summary: Traveling through the realms of Skyrim, I stumbled upon an Irish Beauty.  Georgetta the Irish Princess.
descriptionHtml: Yes you guessed it another female follower mod.  I used my wife as a reference, so be nice to her.  Her name is Georgetta and she mostly hangs out in the Temple of Kynareth in Whiterun.  She is fascinated by the Healing Powers and would love to help repair the damage to the Gildegreen tree.  She has a CBBE body and uses HDT, KS Hair and Young Nord face.  She is Stand Alone and Sultry Voiced.
author: imlords007
